snippet.title: Sundered - Nyarlathotep Boss Reveal | PS4
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/en-us/games/sundered-ps4/

Sundered is a horrifying fight for survival and sanity. 
www.thunderlotusgames.com

It is a replayable metroidvania where you resist or embrace ancient eldritch powers. Nyarlathotep is Sundered's fourth boss. Resist or embrace.
